---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
import VideoComponent from '../components/VdeoComponent.astro';
//import Engineering from './engineering.astro';

const d = new Date()
const whatDay = d.getDay()

const videoUrl ="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uNpphfKB7fA"


---

<Layout title="Special Minds Aarhus @ Github">
	<main class="">
		<h1 class="mt-8 !mb-8">PC Builder Simulator</h1>
		<h2 class="mt-8 mb-[unset] text-center font-thin">Et spil hvor du bygge PC'er for kunder i karrieremode</h2><br>
    	<div class="instructions text-center">
			<iframe 
			width="560" 
			src={videoUrl} 
			title="YouTube video player" 
			frameborder="0" 
			allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
			allowfullscreen
			class="w-full aspect-video"
		  />
		  <br><br>
		 <p class=" text-md font-thin mt-0"><span class="font-semibold">Hvorfor </span> 
			Spille PC Builder Simulator 2?<br><br>
			<span class="font-semibold">Fordi </span>  du lære at arbejde med hardware. Bliver introduceret til de forskelige dele og hvad disse består af. Lære at vælge de dele der løser en given opgave bedst, hvad disse dele kan og hvordan du sætter dem i maskinen. <br>
			Altsammen på en sjov måde i spilformat
			<br><br>
				<div class="p-8 mb-8 rounded-lg border-2 border-white border-solid">

					<p class=" text-2xl font-bold mt-0 ">Installation</p>	
					<p class="text-md font-thin mt-0 ">
						<a class="!no-underline" href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/621060/PC_Building_Simulator/">
						1) Finde spillet på steam 
						</a>
						<br>
						<a class="!no-underline text-sm" href="https://store.epicgames.com/da/p/pc-building-simulator-2--demo">
						Alternativt: Download via hjemmeside og spil det via Epic Game Luncher<br>
							</a>
						<br>
							2) Download/køb <span class="!font-medium">demoen</span> - Du kan spille karrieremode helt op til level 5 
							<br>
						<span class="text-sm">Tal med underviser hvis du gerne vil spille mere end level 5. Det kan du godt!</span>
							<br><br>
					</p> 
				</div>
				
		
				<iframe 
			width="560" 
			src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PsqulPtiR3g" 
			title="YouTube video player" 
			frameborder="0" 
			allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
			allowfullscreen
			class="w-full aspect-video mb-6"
		  />
		
			<div class="p-8 mb-8 rounded-lg border-2 border-white border-solid">

					<p class=" text-2xl font-bold mt-0 ">Spil spillet</p>	
					<p class="text-md font-thin mt-0 ">
						1) Se videoen oven for - for at få mest muligt ud af spillet  
						<br>
						<span class="text-sm text-center">Note: Du må gerne dele video op i små bidder <br>og/eller vende tilbage til den, når du f.eks. skal arbejde en GPU i spillet<br> </span><br>
						<a class="!no-underline" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f_6Wau9WExk">
						2) Spil. Lær. Ha' det sjovt!
						</a>
						<br>
						
					</p> 
					
					
				</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		width: 800px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: white;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	a{
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	.astro-a {
		position: absolute;
		top: -32px;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translatex(-50%);
		width: 220px;
		height: auto;
		z-index: -1;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.125;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}
	.text-gradient {
		background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}
	.instructions {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		
	}
	.instructions.color{

	}
	.instructions code {
		font-size: 0.8em;
		font-weight: bold;
		background: rgba(var(--accent-light), 12%);
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		border-radius: 4px;
		padding: 0.3em 0.4em;
	}
	.instructions strong {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
	}
	.link-card-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(1fr, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 0;
	}
</style>
